        {
            "text": "[SCREECHING TIRES]", 
            "dur": "11.716", 
            "start": "0"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "CHRIS HARRIS: This is the brief\nstory of our trip to", 
            "dur": "2.06", 
            "start": "11.716"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "visit Pagani and drive\nthe Huayra.", 
            "dur": "3.03", 
            "start": "13.776"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "These are crazy smash-and-grab\nraids, really.", 
            "dur": "3.11", 
            "start": "16.806"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Shoot what you can, live for the\nmoment, and a part of me", 
            "dur": "3.94", 
            "start": "19.916"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "exists purely for this.", 
            "dur": "1.801", 
            "start": "23.856"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[AIRPORT NOISES]", 
            "dur": "1.413", 
            "start": "25.657"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "CHRIS HARRIS: We just\nlanded in Bologna.", 
            "dur": "1.413", 
            "start": "27.07"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the baggage carousel isn&#39;t\neven whirring yet.", 
            "dur": "6.442", 
            "start": "28.483"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I think there&#39;s only\none plane landed.", 
            "dur": "1.479", 
            "start": "34.925"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So in fact it&#39;s right beside\nthe terminal building.", 
            "dur": "2.958", 
            "start": "36.404"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I&#39;m just wondering where our\nbags are with 200 other", 
            "dur": "3.844", 
            "start": "39.362"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "people, having just been thrown\naround like a rag doll", 
            "dur": "2.458", 
            "start": "43.206"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "on BA 666 from Gatwick.", 
            "dur": "3.992", 
            "start": "45.664"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Pleasant way to travel,\nbut I&#39;m excited", 
            "dur": "2.594", 
            "start": "49.656"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because you know what?", 
            "dur": "0.3", 
            "start": "52.25"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m coming to Italy, coming\nto [INAUDIBLE]", 
            "dur": "2.096", 
            "start": "52.55"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Valley in Bologna, driving\nto LeMans.", 
            "dur": "2.495", 
            "start": "54.646"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That&#39;s always special.", 
            "dur": "0.998", 
            "start": "57.141"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ve not been here for a long\ntime, largely because Ferrari", 
            "dur": "3.232", 
            "start": "58.139"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "doesn&#39;t run anymore.", 
            "dur": "0.485", 
            "start": "61.371"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But that&#39;s another story.", 
            "dur": "1.455", 
            "start": "61.856"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So why is it, whenever you book\na hired car, you always", 
            "dur": "3.335", 
            "start": "67.191"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "book the one with\na massive queue.", 
            "dur": "2.18", 
            "start": "70.526"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then look, there&#39;s Sixt.", 
            "dur": "2.12", 
            "start": "72.706"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There&#39;s about four others\ndown there.", 
            "dur": "1.644", 
            "start": "74.826"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Is there someone out there to\ncheck the car over before?", 
            "dur": "3.016", 
            "start": "76.47"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "HERTZ EMPLOYEE: No.", 
            "dur": "0.665", 
            "start": "79.486"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But there are some\nmarks on it.", 
            "dur": "1.721", 
            "start": "80.151"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "If you find other marks\njust contact us.", 
            "dur": "3.864", 
            "start": "81.872"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "About those, don&#39;t worry.", 
            "dur": "3.381", 
            "start": "85.736"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "CHRIS HARRIS: We didn&#39;t get sat\nnav because my credit card", 
            "dur": "2.639", 
            "start": "89.117"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "would have bounced.", 
            "dur": "0.88", 
            "start": "91.756"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And being Italian, he told me\nthat he wouldn&#39;t charge me if", 
            "dur": "2.73", 
            "start": "92.636"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "there were only small scratches\non the car, which", 
            "dur": "2.14", 
            "start": "95.366"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "means he will charge me.", 
            "dur": "2.29", 
            "start": "97.506"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Rental car bingo-- so we don&#39;t\nknow what we&#39;re going to get.", 
            "dur": "1.74", 
            "start": "99.796"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I ticked the box for the\ncheapest, cheapest car, of", 
            "dur": "2.66", 
            "start": "101.536"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "course, as you do.", 
            "dur": "1.402", 
            "start": "104.196"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I&#39;m thinking Fiat Panda,\nwould you reckon?", 
            "dur": "2.188", 
            "start": "105.598"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "No?", 
            "dur": "1.01", 
            "start": "107.786"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Fiat Panda?", 
            "dur": "1.43", 
            "start": "108.796"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MALE SPEAKER (OFFSCREEN):\nYeah, that", 
            "dur": "0.7", 
            "start": "110.226"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "sounds like a good shot.", 
            "dur": "0.6", 
            "start": "110.926"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Maybe we could squeeze all of\nour kit and that in the 500.", 
            "dur": "3.135", 
            "start": "111.526"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "CHRIS HARRIS: OK.", 
            "dur": "1.245", 
            "start": "114.661"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Where is Hertz?", 
            "dur": "0.85", 
            "start": "115.906"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "MALE SPEAKER (OFFSCREEN):\nBlip the key.", 
            "dur": "1.53", 
            "start": "116.756"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "CHRIS HARRIS: Hertz.", 
            "dur": "1.47", 
            "start": "118.286"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Hertz.", 
            "dur": "2.94", 
            "start": "119.756"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "59.", 
            "dur": "2.94", 
            "start": "122.696"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "There she is.", 
            "dur": "3.43", 
            "start": "125.636"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Panda.", 
            "dur": "1.96", 
            "start": "129.066"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Some marks on it?", 
            "dur": "1.96", 
            "start": "131.026"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Fucking hell.", 
            "dur": "2.94", 
            "start": "132.986"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[LAUGHTER]", 
            "dur": "0.52", 
            "start": "135.926"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "CHRIS HARRIS: He described it\nas some small marks, and it", 
            "dur": "3.71", 
            "start": "136.446"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "needs reshelling.", 
            "dur": "0.96", 
            "start": "140.156"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[LAUGHTER]", 
            "dur": "2.94", 
            "start": "141.116"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "CHRIS HARRIS: What else\nis wrong with it?", 
            "dur": "2.45", 
            "start": "144.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Look at this.", 
            "dur": "0.59", 
            "start": "149.936"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is why this country&#39;s\nbrilliant.", 
            "dur": "1.13", 
            "start": "150.526"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I just went in there and said,\nlook, the hired car&#39;s", 
            "dur": "1.41", 
            "start": "151.656"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "completely knackered, and\nit&#39;s got massive damage.", 
            "dur": "2.21", 
            "start": "153.066"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So I wrote, big damage.", 
            "dur": "2.74", 
            "start": "155.276"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And the guy just said, yeah,\ndon&#39;t worry about it.", 
            "dur": "2.62", 
            "start": "158.016"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "From the airport, it&#39;s a\n20-minute wobble in the", 
            "dur": "2.49", 
            "start": "160.636"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "shacked Fiat, then dinner with\nthe chap who has the fastest", 
            "dur": "3.42", 
            "start": "163.126"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "name in the world--", 
            "dur": "2.23", 
            "start": "166.546"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Luca Venturi, Pagani&#39;s PR man.", 
            "dur": "3.38", 
            "start": "168.776"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And wouldn&#39;t you know it, as we\ndiscussed aerodynamics and", 
            "dur": "2.38", 
            "start": "172.156"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "weight distribution over steak\nand balsamic vinegar, test", 
            "dur": "2.75", 
            "start": "174.536"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "driver Davide Testi--", 
            "dur": "1.68", 
            "start": "177.286"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "a man with another very,\nvery quick name--", 
            "dur": "3.07", 
            "start": "178.966"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "pops by on his way home.", 
            "dur": "1.92", 
            "start": "182.036"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The owner of the restaurant\nimmediately absconds from his", 
            "dur": "2.25", 
            "start": "183.956"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "duties for a photo\nwith the car.", 
            "dur": "2.03", 
            "start": "186.206"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In fact, everyone photographs\nthis remarkable-looking", 
            "dur": "3.22", 
            "start": "188.236"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "machine, including me.", 
            "dur": "2.13", 
            "start": "191.456"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then Davide leaves\nas only an Italian", 
            "dur": "3.27", 
            "start": "193.586"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "test driver can leave.", 
            "dur": "2.167", 
            "start": "196.856"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[PUNCHES THE GAS]", 
            "dur": "6.227", 
            "start": "199.023"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "CHRIS HARRIS: Next morning, it&#39;s\noff to the Pagani factory", 
            "dur": "2.866", 
            "start": "205.25"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and an introduction from the man\nhimself, Horacio Pagani,", 
            "dur": "3.35", 
            "start": "208.116"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "who always talks about his\ncreations with the zeal and", 
            "dur": "3.45", 
            "start": "211.466"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "passion of a father displaying\nhis newborn child.", 
            "dur": "3.9", 
            "start": "214.916"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Better still, the tall bloke to\nthe right is Ola Kallenius,", 
            "dur": "2.49", 
            "start": "218.816"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the boss of AMG, which builds\nthe Huayra&#39;s twin-turbo V12.", 
            "dur": "4.55", 
            "start": "221.306"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "He was in town to experience\nthe car for the first time.", 
            "dur": "2.985", 
            "start": "225.856"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "OLA KALLENIUS: Zonda&#39;s good.", 
            "dur": "1.045", 
            "start": "228.841"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is better.", 
            "dur": "1.491", 
            "start": "229.886"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But I have to look at the fine\nprint of my contract.", 
            "dur": "3.976", 
            "start": "231.377"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[LAUGHING]", 
            "dur": "2.982", 
            "start": "235.353"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "CHRIS HARRIS: But there&#39;s only\nso much talking you can do in", 
            "dur": "3.011", 
            "start": "238.335"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the presence of a\ncar like this.", 
            "dur": "2.43", 
            "start": "241.346"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "First, you want to be on your\nown with it, to drink in that", 
            "dur": "3.95", 
            "start": "243.776"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "shape and those incredible\ndished rear wheels.", 
            "dur": "4.55", 
            "start": "247.726"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And then, you have to just\ngo and drive it.", 
            "dur": "3.009", 
            "start": "252.276"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[MUSIC PLAYING]", 
            "dur": "40.672", 
            "start": "257.862"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[ENGINE REVVING]", 
            "dur": "2.48", 
            "start": "298.534"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "CHRIS HARRIS: So finally,\nI&#39;m driving the Huayra.", 
            "dur": "4.33", 
            "start": "319.366"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That&#39;s the first\npoint to make.", 
            "dur": "1.16", 
            "start": "323.696"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s called the &quot;Why-Rah,&quot; not\nthe &quot;Why-Ar-Uh&quot; or the", 
            "dur": "2.9", 
            "start": "324.856"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "&quot;Why-ee-Rah&quot; or the &quot;Hee-Ar-Uh.&quot;\nIt&#39;s Huayra.", 
            "dur": "3.976", 
            "start": "327.756"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "One day I&#39;ll learn to\nsay it properly.", 
            "dur": "2.014", 
            "start": "331.732"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Mr. Pagani probably doesn&#39;t like\nthe way I say it, but I&#39;m", 
            "dur": "2.61", 
            "start": "333.746"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "trying, OK, Horacio,\nI&#39;m trying.", 
            "dur": "2.86", 
            "start": "336.356"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What do I think about\nthis car?", 
            "dur": "2.43", 
            "start": "339.216"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Rather predictably,\nit&#39;s not like", 
            "dur": "1.18", 
            "start": "341.646"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "anything else I&#39;ve driven.", 
            "dur": "1.7", 
            "start": "342.826"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m now on quite a bumpy, quite\nopen A road in Italy.", 
            "dur": "3.65", 
            "start": "344.526"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ve got quite supple\nsuspension.", 
            "dur": "1.405", 
            "start": "348.176"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ve got a gearbox that&#39;s\nrunning in automatic mode.", 
            "dur": "3.655", 
            "start": "349.581"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And actually, even though I&#39;ve\ngot seven gears, because of", 
            "dur": "3.06", 
            "start": "353.236"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the torque on offer, I need\nabout three gears.", 
            "dur": "3.85", 
            "start": "356.296"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is a car that\nis easy to drive.", 
            "dur": "2.47", 
            "start": "360.146"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That&#39;s the first point.", 
            "dur": "0.42", 
            "start": "362.616"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s easy to drive.", 
            "dur": "1.44", 
            "start": "363.036"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Why is it easy to drive?", 
            "dur": "1.2", 
            "start": "364.476"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Well, there&#39;s so much torque--", 
            "dur": "1.5", 
            "start": "365.676"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "1,000 Newton-meters.", 
            "dur": "2.65", 
            "start": "367.176"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Get that?", 
            "dur": "0.59", 
            "start": "369.826"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That&#39;s 737 foot-pounds of torque\nin a car that weights", 
            "dur": "3.95", 
            "start": "370.416"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "1,350 kilograms dry.", 
            "dur": "2.735", 
            "start": "374.366"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "That&#39;s outrageous.", 
            "dur": "1.31", 
            "start": "377.101"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it means that you just\nsqueeze the throttle.", 
            "dur": "1.985", 
            "start": "378.411"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The boost builds at around 2,000\nrpm, and you don&#39;t have", 
            "dur": "3.368", 
            "start": "380.396"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to think about it.", 
            "dur": "1.512", 
            "start": "383.764"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Pedal weights are quite heavy,\nobviously only two pedals.", 
            "dur": "2.555", 
            "start": "385.276"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But for me, one of the reasons\nwhy this car is easy to drive", 
            "dur": "2.765", 
            "start": "387.831"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is the steering.", 
            "dur": "1.3", 
            "start": "390.596"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s very, very accurate, and\nit&#39;s very precise, and it&#39;s", 
            "dur": "2.61", 
            "start": "391.896"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "got a good amount of feel.", 
            "dur": "1.85", 
            "start": "394.506"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And that means that you\ncan place the car.", 
            "dur": "1.73", 
            "start": "396.356"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And these massive hypercars,\nyou&#39;ve got to be confident", 
            "dur": "2.39", 
            "start": "398.086"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that you&#39;re not just going to\ntake the sides off to be able", 
            "dur": "2.42", 
            "start": "400.476"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "to drive it properly\non the road.", 
            "dur": "1.04", 
            "start": "402.896"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So that&#39;s what I&#39;ve got.", 
            "dur": "1.75", 
            "start": "403.936"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;ve got a car that is perfectly\nrelaxing to drive.", 
            "dur": "3.18", 
            "start": "405.686"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It rides well enough.", 
            "dur": "1.12", 
            "start": "408.866"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The cabin is big and airy.", 
            "dur": "1.58", 
            "start": "409.986"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And whereas an Aventador is kind\nof up and at you and you", 
            "dur": "2.27", 
            "start": "411.566"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "feel like you&#39;re stuck in\nbetween, wedged in between", 
            "dur": "2.82", 
            "start": "413.836"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "great big amounts of face sheer\nand center console, this", 
            "dur": "2.93", 
            "start": "416.656"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "is big and open.", 
            "dur": "0.94", 
            "start": "419.586"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "My knee can move in front\nof the center console.", 
            "dur": "2.22", 
            "start": "420.526"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And of course, the quality of\nthe cabin and the jewelry", 
            "dur": "3.09", 
            "start": "422.746"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that&#39;s going on here\nis just staggering.", 
            "dur": "1.51", 
            "start": "425.836"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You know that.", 
            "dur": "0.95", 
            "start": "427.346"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m going to have a look at that\nnow because we need to", 
            "dur": "1.8", 
            "start": "428.296"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "celebrate the details\non this car.", 
            "dur": "5.25", 
            "start": "430.096"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Carbon, polished metal, and\nleather meet in one great,", 
            "dur": "4.13", 
            "start": "435.346"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "writhing lump of loveliness.", 
            "dur": "2.56", 
            "start": "439.476"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The clock faces are illegible.", 
            "dur": "1.26", 
            "start": "442.036"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But the central readout is\nelectronic and clear.", 
            "dur": "2.76", 
            "start": "443.296"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The wheel is nearly perfect\nin shape and size.", 
            "dur": "2.8", 
            "start": "446.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The pedals feel good.", 
            "dur": "0.85", 
            "start": "448.856"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But the stumpy gear lever\nis almost too", 
            "dur": "2.67", 
            "start": "449.706"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "cool not to use itself.", 
            "dur": "2.32", 
            "start": "452.376"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The signature quad exhausts are\nin pure titanium, and the", 
            "dur": "2.74", 
            "start": "454.696"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "system weighs just\n12 kilograms.", 
            "dur": "3.04", 
            "start": "457.436"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Suspension is identical to the\nZonda R, which lapped the ring", 
            "dur": "3.61", 
            "start": "460.476"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in six minutes and 47 seconds.", 
            "dur": "3.39", 
            "start": "464.086"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The car has around 730\nhorsepower from a six-liter,", 
            "dur": "2.805", 
            "start": "467.476"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "twin-turbo V12 by AMG.", 
            "dur": "2.935", 
            "start": "470.281"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s a bespoke engine\nfor Pagani.", 
            "dur": "1.97", 
            "start": "473.216"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it has its own internal\ncode-- for", 
            "dur": "2.172", 
            "start": "475.186"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "geeks like me, M158--", 
            "dur": "2.428", 
            "start": "477.358"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "like that.", 
            "dur": "1.67", 
            "start": "479.786"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s a massively impressive\npower plant.", 
            "dur": "2.21", 
            "start": "481.456"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And of course, that&#39;s the\nbrilliance of Pagani.", 
            "dur": "2.02", 
            "start": "483.666"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Rather than going out and trying\nto do his own engine,", 
            "dur": "2.49", 
            "start": "485.686"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "he&#39;s using something that he\nknows works from a company", 
            "dur": "2.05", 
            "start": "488.176"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that has kind of unprecedented\nskill at making massive", 
            "dur": "2.06", 
            "start": "490.226"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "horsepower.", 
            "dur": "0.94", 
            "start": "492.286"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So the AMG power plant is\ncrucial to this package.", 
            "dur": "3.704", 
            "start": "493.226"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Perhaps the key issue around\nthe Huayra is the noise, or", 
            "dur": "4.406", 
            "start": "496.93"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "rather lack of it, or\nrather presence of", 
            "dur": "2.62", 
            "start": "501.336"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "turbocharged noise.", 
            "dur": "0.6", 
            "start": "503.956"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Being turbocharged, this car\njust cannot sound like those", 
            "dur": "3.5", 
            "start": "504.556"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "amazing Zondas we had before,\nparticularly that last R", 
            "dur": "3.254", 
            "start": "508.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "version, which just sounded like\nall sorts of bad things", 
            "dur": "3.086", 
            "start": "511.31"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "going wrong in the right way.", 
            "dur": "2", 
            "start": "514.396"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So we have turbo noise\nthis time.", 
            "dur": "1.099", 
            "start": "516.396"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Here, I&#39;ll give you some.", 
            "dur": "0.991", 
            "start": "517.495"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Get a load of this.", 
            "dur": "3.028", 
            "start": "518.486"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[ENGINE NOISE]", 
            "dur": "3.702", 
            "start": "521.514"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "CHRIS HARRIS: Interestingly,\nPagani has worked hard to try", 
            "dur": "1.79", 
            "start": "525.216"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and tune that noise.", 
            "dur": "0.81", 
            "start": "527.006"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s the first turbocharged car\nthat I&#39;ve driven that has", 
            "dur": "3.22", 
            "start": "527.816"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "got deliberately tuned\nturbocharged noise.", 
            "dur": "1.37", 
            "start": "531.036"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And there&#39;s wastegate\nrattles and fizzles.", 
            "dur": "1.777", 
            "start": "532.406"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And there&#39;s lots going on.", 
            "dur": "1.983", 
            "start": "534.183"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Does it sound as\ngood as Zonda?", 
            "dur": "1.546", 
            "start": "536.166"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "No.", 
            "dur": "0.344", 
            "start": "537.712"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s a different noise and one\nthat I think over time could", 
            "dur": "3.1", 
            "start": "538.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "become quite special.", 
            "dur": "1.374", 
            "start": "541.156"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So to turn the Huayra into\nsomething that is actually not", 
            "dur": "2.68", 
            "start": "545.736"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "that friendly and is a full-on\nsupercar, hypercar experience,", 
            "dur": "3.29", 
            "start": "548.416"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "there&#39;s a button here\nthat says ESC.", 
            "dur": "2.01", 
            "start": "551.706"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You get it in sport mode, and\nyou hold it down for 5", 
            "dur": "2.01", 
            "start": "553.716"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "seconds, and you hear\na little BINK.", 
            "dur": "1.99", 
            "start": "555.726"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And you look at the dashboard,\nand it says ESC Off.", 
            "dur": "4.836", 
            "start": "557.716"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And you get a little squiggle\nsign on there.", 
            "dur": "2.17", 
            "start": "562.552"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And now you&#39;re on your own.", 
            "dur": "4.884", 
            "start": "564.722"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So, second gear coming\nup this rather narrow", 
            "dur": "4.37", 
            "start": "569.606"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "mountain pass of a road.", 
            "dur": "2.54", 
            "start": "573.976"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Front end is great.", 
            "dur": "1.55", 
            "start": "576.516"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But the performance is nuts.", 
            "dur": "1.996", 
            "start": "578.066"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Oh, yes, Ha!", 
            "dur": "1.146", 
            "start": "584.556"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Ha!", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "585.702"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Front is really good.", 
            "dur": "0.68", 
            "start": "590.946"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So we&#39;ve got no understeer\nreally, but coming out--", 
            "dur": "4.798", 
            "start": "591.626"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "it&#39;s spooling up everywhere.", 
            "dur": "3.624", 
            "start": "596.424"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s just nuts.", 
            "dur": "2.788", 
            "start": "600.048"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Steering&#39;s a bit slow for\nthese sorts of roads.", 
            "dur": "3.295", 
            "start": "602.836"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "As you can see, I have\nto work quite hard.", 
            "dur": "2.955", 
            "start": "606.131"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s an animal, guys.", 
            "dur": "1.84", 
            "start": "615.956"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s an absolute animal.", 
            "dur": "2.302", 
            "start": "617.796"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Woohoohoohoo!", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "625.078"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Woohoohoohoo!", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "634.54"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What a machine.", 
            "dur": "0.866", 
            "start": "642.046"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I mean, the fact that it&#39;s\ntwo-wheel drive as well.", 
            "dur": "5.619", 
            "start": "642.912"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "So yeah, the billionaire can\ndrive it in automatic mode.", 
            "dur": "3.765", 
            "start": "651.211"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But I&#39;ll tell you what, if\nyou want to be a hooligan", 
            "dur": "6.242", 
            "start": "654.976"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "woohoohoohoo!", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "661.218"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What a machine.", 
            "dur": "1.325", 
            "start": "673.526"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I can&#39;t say too much.", 
            "dur": "1.088", 
            "start": "674.851"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m just going to concentrate\non driving it.", 
            "dur": "3.691", 
            "start": "675.939"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "God, it&#39;s fast.", 
            "dur": "1.781", 
            "start": "679.63"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Does it feel like\n730 horsepower?", 
            "dur": "2.285", 
            "start": "681.411"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It feels like more to me.", 
            "dur": "1.29", 
            "start": "683.696"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When the boost comes,\nit&#39;s furious.", 
            "dur": "1.66", 
            "start": "689.406"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And you just hang on.", 
            "dur": "2.39", 
            "start": "691.066"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You really do.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "693.456"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s fast.", 
            "dur": "1.54", 
            "start": "703.176"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s fast.", 
            "dur": "2.58", 
            "start": "704.716"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And there&#39;s flaps going off and\nthere&#39;s all sorts of drama", 
            "dur": "3.009", 
            "start": "707.296"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "and theater.", 
            "dur": "3.283", 
            "start": "710.305"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "This is just pure hypercar.", 
            "dur": "5.698", 
            "start": "713.588"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And anyone that thinks that\nPagani&#39;s gone soft needs to", 
            "dur": "5.03", 
            "start": "719.286"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "come and sit in this now.", 
            "dur": "1.74", 
            "start": "724.316"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because this is power to weight\nratio through two", 
            "dur": "5.165", 
            "start": "726.056"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "driven wheels with--", 
            "dur": "2.125", 
            "start": "731.221"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "wait for it--", 
            "dur": "0.89", 
            "start": "733.346"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "no traction control.", 
            "dur": "1.25", 
            "start": "734.236"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s a tonic.", 
            "dur": "1.2", 
            "start": "753.546"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I need to back away\nfor a minute,", 
            "dur": "2.15", 
            "start": "754.746"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "because that&#39;s so full-on.", 
            "dur": "3.54", 
            "start": "756.896"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You want to match that, you&#39;ve\ngot to buy yourself a needle", 
            "dur": "2.22", 
            "start": "760.436"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "with some brown stuff in\nit because that is just", 
            "dur": "2.882", 
            "start": "762.656"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "remarkable.", 
            "dur": "1.968", 
            "start": "765.538"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Is that legal?", 
            "dur": "1.48", 
            "start": "767.506"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I&#39;m sure it is, but\nJesus Christ.", 
            "dur": "3.63", 
            "start": "768.986"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "730 horsepower, two wheels,\nno traction control.", 
            "dur": "5.19", 
            "start": "772.616"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Horacio, I salute you.", 
            "dur": "1.99", 
            "start": "777.806"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I needed time to cool my oil\ntemperature after that.", 
            "dur": "3.46", 
            "start": "784.556"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And here&#39;s the nitty-gritty.", 
            "dur": "1.64", 
            "start": "788.016"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Yes, the steering is great.", 
            "dur": "1.82", 
            "start": "789.656"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But so is the damping with the\nmanually adjustable Ohlins", 
            "dur": "2.69", 
            "start": "791.476"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "shocks set to pretty soft.", 
            "dur": "2.17", 
            "start": "794.166"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The ceramic breaks have decent\nfeel and earn their keep.", 
            "dur": "3.76", 
            "start": "796.336"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Pedal lift is pretty\nhigh though.", 
            "dur": "2.45", 
            "start": "800.096"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The seven-speed extract\ngearbox is a peach--", 
            "dur": "2.48", 
            "start": "802.546"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "fast and enjoyable in manual\nmode, yet weighs just 96", 
            "dur": "3.48", 
            "start": "805.026"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "kilograms and is mounted\ntransversely.", 
            "dur": "2.35", 
            "start": "808.506"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "The powertrain package is neater\nthan the Zonda, so the", 
            "dur": "3.06", 
            "start": "810.856"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "weight distribution is\na perfect 50/50.", 
            "dur": "3.27", 
            "start": "813.916"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And as for the active\naerodynamics, I didn&#39;t go fast", 
            "dur": "2.05", 
            "start": "817.186"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "enough to test them.", 
            "dur": "1.75", 
            "start": "819.236"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But who cares when they\nlook so damn cool?", 
            "dur": "2.065", 
            "start": "820.986"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "When I first saw the Huayra, I\nwasn&#39;t entirely convinced.", 
            "dur": "2.53", 
            "start": "831.396"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because I didn&#39;t think the\nstyling was quite as cute as", 
            "dur": "2.25", 
            "start": "833.926"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "the Zonda, and I was worried\nabout this twin", 
            "dur": "2.31", 
            "start": "836.176"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "turbocharging aspect.", 
            "dur": "1.56", 
            "start": "838.486"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Now that I&#39;ve driven the car, I\nhave to say I got it wrong.", 
            "dur": "3.11", 
            "start": "840.046"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Do you know what?", 
            "dur": "0.44", 
            "start": "843.156"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "In the flesh, when you park it\nnext to a Zonda, it just looks", 
            "dur": "2.97", 
            "start": "843.596"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "more modern.", 
            "dur": "0.68", 
            "start": "846.566"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It just looks more appealing.", 
            "dur": "0.89", 
            "start": "847.246"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It just looks cleverer.", 
            "dur": "1.24", 
            "start": "848.136"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I&#39;ve never seen a car that&#39;s\nhad so much detail", 
            "dur": "2.71", 
            "start": "849.376"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "lavished on it.", 
            "dur": "0.81", 
            "start": "852.086"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s extraordinary, truly\nextraordinary.", 
            "dur": "2.38", 
            "start": "852.896"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But they haven&#39;t forgotten about\nthe driving experience.", 
            "dur": "2.52", 
            "start": "855.276"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because this is a\nvery clever car.", 
            "dur": "1.88", 
            "start": "857.796"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And I hadn&#39;t quite expected\nthe breadth of talent.", 
            "dur": "2.76", 
            "start": "859.676"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "You can leave all the\nbuttons in place.", 
            "dur": "2.24", 
            "start": "862.436"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And you can leave\nit in automatic.", 
            "dur": "1.16", 
            "start": "864.676"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And it&#39;s entirely usable.", 
            "dur": "1.34", 
            "start": "865.836"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "OK, It&#39;s not a Nissan Micra,\nbut as long as you&#39;ve got a", 
            "dur": "2.36", 
            "start": "867.176"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "modicum of talent, you won&#39;t\nhave a problem mooching around", 
            "dur": "2.99", 
            "start": "869.536"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "in this car, as I explained.", 
            "dur": "1.83", 
            "start": "872.526"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "But if you turn the systems off,\nI can&#39;t think of another", 
            "dur": "2.646", 
            "start": "874.356"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "car like this--", 
            "dur": "0.694", 
            "start": "877.002"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "730 BHP.", 
            "dur": "1.78", 
            "start": "877.696"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "And even bigger torque figure,\ntwo-wheel drive, and", 
            "dur": "3.06", 
            "start": "879.476"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "you&#39;re on your own.", 
            "dur": "0.71", 
            "start": "882.536"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s an animal, as\nyou can see.", 
            "dur": "1.07", 
            "start": "883.246"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I was sweating away, genuinely\nenjoying myself.", 
            "dur": "3.92", 
            "start": "884.316"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "What is this car?", 
            "dur": "1.92", 
            "start": "888.236"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "I suppose it is the definitive\nhypercar.", 
            "dur": "1.58", 
            "start": "890.156"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Because it&#39;s that\nstyle statement.", 
            "dur": "1.885", 
            "start": "891.736"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "It&#39;s that aesthetic statement,\nmixed in with an unforgettable", 
            "dur": "3.835", 
            "start": "893.621"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "driving experience.", 
            "dur": "1.19", 
            "start": "897.456"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "Yeah, love it.", 
            "dur": "3.68", 
            "start": "898.646"
        }, 
        {
            "text": "[ENGINE ROARING]", 
            "dur": "7.79", 
            "start": "907.726"
        }
